+    /// Wrap the given `expr` in `hir::ExprKind::Use`.
+    ///
+    /// In terms of drop order, it has the same effect as
+    /// wrapping `expr` in `{ let _t = $expr; _t }` but
+    /// should provide better compile-time performance.
